Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:11.63,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,Good night, Kosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:11.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,﻿おやすみ　幸介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:17.20,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,Good night, Katsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:17.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おやすみ　克巳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.64,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,Good night, Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おやすみ　優
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:28.65,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,Good night, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:28.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おやすみ　真嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:33.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おやすみ　咲楽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:33.88,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,Good night, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,静かに眠ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:43.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:43.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,行ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:51.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,本日はご足労いただき有り難う御座います
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:55.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Again, this is an unofficial meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:55.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,繰り返しますが　これは非公式の会合です
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:57.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting me here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:57.89,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今日はお招きありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:01.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,How does it feel to be \Nback in your main job?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:01.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,本職に戻ってからの調子はどうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:05.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,Please don't torture our junior staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:05.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの若いもんをあんまり虐めんでいただきたいですな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:08.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ポートマフィアの親分さん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:08.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,Port Mafia's boss-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:12.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,My Elise-chan wants ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:12.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,うちのエリスちゃんがアイスクリームを所望でねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:17.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,政府御用達のいい店でもないかねぇ　種田長官
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Are there any ice cream shops that \Ngovernment workers would recommend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Chief Taneda?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:20.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,That is a heartwarming topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:20.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃあ微笑ましい話ですな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:24.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの官僚達にも土産を持ち帰ってやらんと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:24.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,I need to bring back gifts \Nfor our officials, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:27.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,I bet they would be more than happy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お宅の首級なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:29.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,to see your head on a platter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:29.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,喜ばれるやろなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:34.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,早速ですが　本題に入らせていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,If we may, let us proceed \Nright to the agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:37.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,The Gifted Special Operations \NDivision has two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:39.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,異能特務課拠り　ポートマフィア{\fn方正准雅宋_GBK}鷗{\r}外殿への要求は二点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,requests for Ougai-dono of the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:42.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,First, the Port Mafia will divest themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:45.40,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,先ず私　坂口安吾について一切の関知をせず　危害を加えぬこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,of any interest in myself, Sakaguchi Ango,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,and will not harm my person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:48.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Second, the Port Mafia will dispose of Mimic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:51.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一つは　日本に不法入国した異能犯罪組織ミミックを壊滅させること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:49.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,the gifted criminal organization
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:51.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,that has illegally entered Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:55.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一つ目に関しては問題ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:55.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,I have no qualms with the first request.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:58.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,But I hesitate to agree to the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:58.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でも二つ目は確約しかねるなー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:02.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく怖い連中だからね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:02.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,After all, they are a terrifying bunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:05.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　条件にも拠るがね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:05.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Well, it'd depend on the conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:37.36,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:41.89,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I know what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君が何を考えているかわかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,けどやめるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.55,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことをしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.21,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Even if you do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:49.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことをしても　子ども達は戻ってこない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:49.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Even if I do it, it won't \Nbring the kids back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:52.18,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,They still have numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:52.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,連中はまだ余力を残してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:54.37,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,And they are at...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そして奴らの居場所は…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:57.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,連中の居場所ならもうわかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:57.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I got an invitation, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,招待状が来たからな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:00.82,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:04.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,先程首領が秘密の会合に出席したらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:04.75,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,The Boss just attended a secret meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.19,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It was with the Gifted Special Ops Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:07.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,相手は異能特務課
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:10.67,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,There's something more than this going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:10.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この一件にはまだ何か裏がある
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,There's nothing more going on, Dazai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何かなどないよ　太宰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もう凡て終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,It's all over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:17.75,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:17.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おかしな云い方を許してほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:22.10,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Forgive me for putting it this \Nway, but please hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:23.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でも聞いてくれ　何かに頼るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.77,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You need to rely on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.19,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It can be anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:28.11,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You should wait and see what \Nhappens next, whatever that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:28.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この後に起こる何かに期待するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それはきっとある筈なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.51,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.63,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Hey, Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:37.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,300,0,0,,私が何故ポートマフィアに入ったかわかるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.71,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Do you know why I joined the Port Mafia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:42.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに何かあると期待したからだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:42.14,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I was hoping there'd be \Nsomething in it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.77,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,If you place yourself somewhere \Nclose to raw emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,暴力や死　本能や欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:49.97,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,where you're exposed to violence \Nand death, instinct and desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:50.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,250,0,,そういったむき出しの感情に近い処にいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:52.74,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,you can brush against man's true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:52.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人間の本質に触れることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.22,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I thought that way I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすれば何か…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.74,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I could find a reason to live somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,250,0,,何か生きる理由が見つかると思ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I wanted to become a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は小説家になりたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:09.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,再び人を殺したら　その資格がなくなると思った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:10.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I thought I'd lose my right \Nto do that if I killed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,That's why I stopped killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だから殺しをやめた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:14.31,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だがそれも終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,But all that's come to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.18,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:18.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,行くな　織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:18.24,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:26.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I only want one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:26.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の望みは一つだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:29.79,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いたたたた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:53.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君　何をするんだい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:52.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:56.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと前を見て歩かなきゃ駄目じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,You should look where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:59.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく社長に貰った名探偵道具が…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,You almost ruined the famous detective \Ntools the president gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,探偵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:00.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:02.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,Not just any detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,探偵じゃない　名探偵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,I'm a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,Soon, my name will be known in every\N household throughout Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:07.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,じきに日本中が僕の名前を知ることになる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:11.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,I am the best detective the world \Nhas ever known, Edogawa Rampo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:11.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕こそは世界最高の名探偵　江戸川乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:11.87,Stray Dogs - Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.74,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,すまなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待ったー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,Once you see my ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:17.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の能力を見れば　そんな無下な態度は取れなくなるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,you will not be so rude to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,疑うなら見せてあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,If you doubt me, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どれどれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:29.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to be mean here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君　悪いことは云わない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,but you should not go \Nto where you're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.98,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,目的地に行くのはやめたほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,You should reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,考え直すべきだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,If you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,行ったら君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Rampo,0,0,0,,you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:46.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Do you want me to finish it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,とどめは要るか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:20.87,Stray Dogs - Default,F,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:22.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.96,Stray Dogs - Default,F,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.40,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何か云い残すことはあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:25.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.25,Stray Dogs - Default,F,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:29.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう　戦ってくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.34,Stray Dogs - Default,F,0,0,0,,for fighting us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.60,Stray Dogs - Default,F,0,0,0,,Our leader... is up ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:32.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,司令官はこの先だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.26,Stray Dogs - Default,F,0,0,0,,Please save him, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:37.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼も救ってやってくれ　この地獄から
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.31,Stray Dogs - Default,F,0,0,0,,from this hell..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:41.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　わかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おや　太宰君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Oh? Dazai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:54.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君のほうから来るとは珍しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:54.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,How rare of you to come visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.04,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:08:01.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,首領　織田作を救援する為の異能力者部隊編成の許可をいただきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:08:01.36,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I'd like to request permission to organize \Na gifted squad to save Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いいよ　許可しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:03.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Permission granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　理由を教えてもらえるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,But first, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:13.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今織田作はミミック本拠地で単身に拠る威力偵察を行っています
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.26,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku is currently doing reconnaissance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.93,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,in force by himself at Mimic headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:16.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,このままでは貴重な異能力者である織田作が死にます
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:16.97,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,If we do nothing, he will die, and we \Nwill lose a valuable gifted agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君の思考は理解できる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,I understand your reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:26.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だが織田君は恐らく誰かの救援など望んではいないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:25.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,But I doubt Oda-kun wants \Nto be saved by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それについてはどう思うね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,What do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:36.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Dazai-kun, the leader of an organization \Nis at the pinnacle of that organization
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:34.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰君　首領というのはね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:38.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,組織の頂点であると同時に組織の奴隷だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,and, at the same time, he is its slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:44.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,組織存続の為なら　どんな非道も喜んで行わなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,The leader must be more than willing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:44.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,to commit any atrocity in order to \Nensure the organization's survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.64,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That envelope...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その封筒は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:51.00,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I see. I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　そういうことか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:55.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どこへ行くのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.48,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,To Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作の処へ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:11.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Gide,0,0,0,,"It remains only a single seed."{this part is out of order from the quote}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:16.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一粒の麦　もし地に落ちて死なずば　ただ一つにてあらん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Gide,0,0,0,,"Unless a kernel of wheat falls \Nto the ground and dies,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Gide,0,0,0,,"it remains only a single seed."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,死なば…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Gide,0,0,0,,"But if it dies..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,死なば　多くの実を結ぶべし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,"But if it dies, it produces many seeds."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:26.36,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,John 12:24.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:26.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,『ヨハネ伝』第十二章二十四節
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.20,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,You're more well-read than \Nyou look, Sakunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:30.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,見かけに拠らず博識だな　作之助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.86,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I apologize for the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:34.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,子ども達には申し訳ないことをした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.96,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,But it seems to have been worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だがその価値はあったようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.79,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Your eyes are the same as mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君の目は乃公と同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.93,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Like my subordinates and I,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:45.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乃公や部下と同じ　生存の階段から降りた目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.82,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,you look like someone who has left \Nthe stairway of continued existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:50.22,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Welcome, Sakunosuke, to our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:50.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ようこそ作之助　俺達の世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:09.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,未来の読み合いでは埒が明かないな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:09.18,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,We don't seem to make any progress \Nby just reading our own futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,It seems not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そのようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:28.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば　未来予測など使わずにやり合うだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:28.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Then we just have to duel without \Nusing our predictive abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:29.15,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな　作之助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.87,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,You're right, Sakunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.62,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,You are the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,矢張りお前は最高だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,We have not ended the debate, Dazai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ議論が途中だよ　太宰君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.15,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I've been thinking a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと考えていました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:47.31,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,about the Port Mafia, Mimic, and \Nthe black special ops group...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:47.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ポートマフィアとミミックと黒の特殊部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:51.37,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,or, rather, in this case, the Gifted \NSpecial Operations Division...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:51.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　この場合は異能特務課と云うべきですね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:56.06,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,and who's the one controlling the \Nconflict between the three groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:56.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この三組織を巡る対立は誰が操っていたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:02.17,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,This bold and intricate design \Nwas your handiwork, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:02.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この大胆かつ精緻な絵を描いたのは　首領　あなただ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:06.13,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That black envelope \Ncontains that much value.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:06.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その黒い封筒にはそれだけの価値がある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:11.72,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,No matter how powerful the \NPort Mafia may become,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:11.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ポートマフィアがどれほど強大な力を持っていようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.68,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,we exist in constant fear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:15.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,政府機関である異能特務課の機嫌を損ね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:19.60,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,of displeasing the Gifted Special \NOperations Division and being oppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:19.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,弾圧される可能性に常に怯えていなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.61,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That is why, as the price \Nfor crushing Mimic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だからあなたはミミックを潰す対価として
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.58,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,you negotiated for the \Nissuance of this permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:27.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この証書を発行させる取引を持ちかけた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:32.59,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,This permit, which allows us to \Noperate a gifted organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:32.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,異能組織として活動を許可するこの証書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:36.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Sign 1134,0,0,0,,{\fs20\c&H9D9D9D&\pos(406,280)}Gifted \NBusiness\N Permit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:35.40,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,the Gifted Business Permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,異能開業許可証を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.98,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,最高だ　作之助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.98,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,You're perfect, Sakunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Today, I'm with you all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今日はとことん付き合ってやる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:23.80,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:23.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.55,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これが安吾の云っていた…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:28.55,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,Is this what Ango was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:30.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,異能力の特異点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.80,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,The singularity of the ability?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これが乃公の求めた世界だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.01,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,This is the world I've sought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故求めた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Why did you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:41.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は何故殺しをやめた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:40.92,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Why did you stop killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は小説家になりたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I wanted to become a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:49.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,A man told me that's what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:49.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ある人に云われたんだ　そうすべきだと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,He gave me a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:51.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その人は本をくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:56.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がずっと探していた小説の下巻だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:56.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,It was the last volume of a novel I've \Nbeen seeking for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:04.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Before I read it, he told me \Nthat it's a terrible book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:04.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,読む前に　非道い本だと釘を刺された
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:07.49,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,And how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:07.50,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それで　どうだった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:12.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,It was a wonderful book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.50,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その本は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,{eyecatch - sign is already in English}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:12.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,200,0,,とても素晴らしい本だった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:20.53,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You are the one who helped them \Nenter the country illegally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:20.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,首領　彼らの密入国を裏で手助けしたのはあなただ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.60,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You invited the enemy \Norganization to Yokohama
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:25.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは異能特務課を焦らせ　重い腰を上げさせる為に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:28.43,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,to incite the Gifted Special Operations \NDivision into finally taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:28.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,わざと敵対組織を横浜に招いた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:29.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:34.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　そのおかげでこうして異能開業許可証は手に入り
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:34.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, we now have \Nthe Gifted Business Permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:38.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,The government has, for all practical \Npurposes, ratified our illegal activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:38.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,事実上　政府から非合法活動は認可され
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:44.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,厄介な乱暴者は織田君が命を賭して排除してくれている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:44.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,The troublesome aggressors will be taken \Ncare of by Oda-kun with his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,大金星だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,This is a glorious victory for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:51.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,And yet... Why are you so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:51.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに君は何をそんなに怒っているのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:57.89,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You're the one who let Mimic know about \Nthe orphans under Odasaku's care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:57.89,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作が養っていた孤児達の存在をミミックに密告したのはあなただ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:02.85,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You did it so you could counter \NMimic's leader with Odasaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:02.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作を　ミミックの指揮官に唯一抗しうる異能力者として
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.07,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,the only gifted agent \Nwho could be his match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,敵にぶつける為に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Dazai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:09.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,You need to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君はここに居なさい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:16.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それとも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:22.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,Or is there a logical reason \Nwhy you should go to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:22.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼の許に行く合理的な理由でもあるのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:27.10,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,There are two things I \Nwish to say to you, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,云いたいことが二つあります　首領
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:32.22,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,First, you will not shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:32.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一つ　あなたは私を撃たない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.88,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Nor will you have your \Nsubordinates shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,部下に撃たせることもしない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてそう思うね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.16,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Because you have nothing to gain from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,利益がないからです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:47.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Ou,0,0,0,,I believe you also have nothing to \Ngain by defying me and going to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:47.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君にも私の制止を振り切って　彼の許に行く利益などないと思うが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:50.05,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,As for the second thing, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:50.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それが二つ目です　首領
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:53.22,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,There may be nothing to gain by my actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:53.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに利益はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:57.30,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,but there is one reason why I will still go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私が行く理由は一つです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.59,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It's because he is a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼が友達だからですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:26.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,The last book in the series was wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:28.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その下巻は素晴らしい本だったが　一つだけ欠点があった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:28.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,but there was one flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Several pages had been cut out \Nand removed toward the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,最後に近い数頁が切り取られていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.28,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,Then you write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ならばお前が書け
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:38.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Right before the removed \Nsection, there was this line:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:40.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その下巻の切り取られたシーンの直前にこういう台詞があった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,"People live to save themselves."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:48.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,"You will understand that at the \Nmoment of your own death."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:51.97,sign_22584_208_ON_SCREEN_TEXT__,,0,0,0,,{\fad(779,1)}People live to save themselves. You will understand\N that at the moment of your own death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:45.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人は自分を救済する為に生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:48.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬ間際にそれがわかるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:58.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Now, I think that the man who gave me the \Nbook knew I was a hired killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今になって思う
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:58.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,本をくれたあの男は俺を殺し屋だと知っていたのではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:04.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,He knew, and spoke to me so \Nthat I would stop killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:04.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,知っていて　殺しをやめさせる為に声をかけたのではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:09.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,He told me his name when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:09.50,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に会った時　その男は俺に名乗った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten that name \Nfor a very long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:15.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと忘れていたが　つい最近になって彼の名を思い出した
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:15.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,but I finally remembered \Nwhat it was recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.15,Stray Dogs - Flashback,BoyO,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:18.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは誰なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.67,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,儂か
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:23.08,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,My name is Natsume Souseki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:23.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,儂の名は夏目漱石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:24.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:28.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　その小説にあった著者と　同じ名前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:28.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,He had the same name as \Nthe author of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:34.63,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I was a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:34.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乃公は英雄だった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:40.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,祖国を守ることが自分の天命だと信じて戦った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:40.30,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I fought believing it was my god-given \Ndestiny to protect my homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:45.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,先の大戦で俺達は僅か四十名の部隊で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.02,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,In the last great war,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:48.85,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,my squad of forty defeated six hundred \Nenemies who were holed up in a fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:48.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,砦に籠る六百人の敵を打ち倒した
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:53.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だがそれは味方本部の計略だった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:53.46,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,But that was a setup by \Nour allied headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:58.45,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,At the time, our country was \Nalready entering peace talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:58.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,既にその時　本国では和平交渉が行われており
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:01.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,和平後の敵交通網を奪取という
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.36,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,We were used to commit an unjust \Nact for the military staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:04.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,軍幕僚幹部の不義に利用されたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:04.20,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,by seizing an enemy transportation \Nnetwork after peace was achieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:10.29,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Of course, our actions \Nwere deemed a war crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:10.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,当然俺達の行動は戦争犯罪になった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:15.46,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Our comrades in arms became our enemies \Nnow that we were labeled rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:15.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,同胞が反逆者である俺達の相手となる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,部隊の中には自殺する者もいた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.99,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Some in my unit took their own lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:25.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:28.30,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,But there were those who survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:28.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,死なない者もいた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:34.83,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,We lost our homeland and our honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:35.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達は祖国を失い　誇りを失った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:41.21,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,We became ghosts wandering a wasteland \Nin search of enemies to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:41.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてただ敵を求め　戦い続ける　荒野の死霊となった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:46.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,生き方を変えることは本当にできなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Are you sure you couldn't \Nchange your way of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:50.82,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I swore to my men that \NI would die a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:50.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乃公は軍人として死ぬと仲間に誓った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:53.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以外になるのは不可能だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:53.55,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I cannot become anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:59.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　あるいはできたのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:59.68,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,No... perhaps I could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:05.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,生き方を曲げ　軍人ではない何かになることは可能だったのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:03.74,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I may have been able to reshape my way of life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.95,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,and become someone who wasn't a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.28,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Just like how you stopped killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:09.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が殺しをやめたように
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一つ心残りがある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I have one regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I did not say farewell to my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,友にさよならを云っていない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:22.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,To the man who was my only friend \Nin this world I live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:22.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界で　ただの友人でいてくれた男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,He seemed to have tired of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:27.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界に退屈し　ずっと死を待っているように見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,and was waiting for death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:32.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その男は乃公と同じように死を求めていたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:32.45,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Was he in search of death like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:34.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:34.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いいや
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I think it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,違うと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,作之助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.32,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Sakunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:56.38,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Even your last shot was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:56.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,最後まで　素晴らしい弾丸だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:08.57,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:08.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.61,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You're an idiot, Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.79,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,莫迦だよ　織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君は大莫迦だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:20.82,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You're a complete idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:21.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.20,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Why did you go along with what he wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:26.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな奴に付き合うなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Dazai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:31.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に云っておきたいことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,There's something I want to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だ　やめてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:33.43,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:34.50,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.46,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ助かるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.53,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You might still make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　きっと助かる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.96,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,No, you {\i1}will{\i0} make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だからそんな風に…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.15,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,So don't talk like—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は云ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:46.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You told me that you might \Nfind a reason to live
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:50.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,暴力と流血の世界にいれば　生きる理由が見つかるかもしれないと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:50.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,if you lived in a world of \Nviolence and bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.74,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　云った
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:53.33,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But who cares what I said now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:53.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,云ったがそんなこと今は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You won't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:55.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,見つからないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,自分でもわかっている筈だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You must know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Whether you're on the side who kills people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:03.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人を殺す側だろうと　救う側だろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,or the side who saves people,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:06.40,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の予測を超えるものは現れない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:06.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,nothing beyond what you \Nwould expect will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:13.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Nothing in this world can fill \Nthat lonely hole you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:13.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の孤独を埋めるものは　この世のどこにもない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:18.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You will wander the darkness for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:18.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は永遠に闇の中を彷徨う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.81,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私はどうすればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:27.53,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Be on the side that saves people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人を救う側になれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:37.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どちらも同じなら　いい人間になれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,If both sides are the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,become a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:40.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,弱者を救い　孤児を守れ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:40.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Save the weak, and protect the orphans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:45.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,正義も悪もお前には大差ないだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:45.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Neither good nor evil means \Nmuch to you, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:49.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,but that'd make you at \Nleast a little bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:49.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そのほうが幾分か素敵だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:52.68,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,How do you know that for sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故わかる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:54.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Of course I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:57.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,わかるさ　誰よりもわかる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:57.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I know better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:02.89,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はお前の友達だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:02.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Because... I am your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:08.76,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:10.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,わかった　そうしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:10.48,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:17.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人は自分を救済する為に存在するか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:17.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,People exist to save themselves, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:22.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにその通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:22.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,How true...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:58.04,sign_31489_292_Two_Weeks_Later,Sign 2154,0,0,0,,{\fad(779,1)}Two Weeks Later
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:09.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,200,0,,内務省の重鎮がこんな安酒場で独り手酌とは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:07.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,I didn't think a heavyweight in \Nthe Ministry of Internal Affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,would be drinking alone \Nin a cheap bar like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:13.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,寂しい限りですな　種田長官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:13.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,How lonesome, Chief Taneda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:14.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:14.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君は…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:16.11,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Now, now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まあまあまあまあまあ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:20.46,TEXT-JP-ja,,1050,0,0,,暫く行方を眩ませとったと噂で聞いたが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:20.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,I heard rumors that you had \Ngone underground for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:24.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,転職先を探してましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:24.60,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I'm looking for a new job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:27.52,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Do you know of any good positions?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:27.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかお勧めはありませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:30.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,Do you wish to join the Gifted Special \NOperations Division? If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,特務課を希望かな　それなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:33.17,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I regretfully decline the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:33.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そちらのほうは辞退しますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:35.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,規則の多い職場は肌に合わなくてね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:35.87,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I don't do too well in a workplace \Nthat has a lot of regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:38.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,Then what are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:38.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,では　何が希望かね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:41.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人助けができる処
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:41.62,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Somewhere I can help people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,聞きたいことは山ほどあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:50.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,I have a lot of questions for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:53.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君の経歴は汚れ過ぎとる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:53.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,Your history is too sordid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:57.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,You'll have to go underground for at \Nleast two years to get a blank slate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:57.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,洗う為には二年ほど地下に潜る必要があるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:23:01.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,But I suppose I {\i1}may{\i0} have a lead...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:01.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だがまあ　心当たりがないわけでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:06.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,伺いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:06.53,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.81,0:23:12.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,異能力者を集めた武装組織だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.88,0:23:12.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,There is an armed organization \Nof gifted individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:17.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,They take on cases that are in a legal gray \Nzone and are untouchable by civil workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:17.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,公僕には頼れぬ灰色の厄介事を引き受け　解決する
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:21.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そこの社長は心ある男でな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:21.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,The company president is a man of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:24.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君の希望に添うかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:24.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Tane,0,0,0,,You may find him in alignment \Nwith what you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:30.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人を救う仕事ができますか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:31.06,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡花ちゃんの武装探偵社での初めての仕事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.22,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Can I do work that saves people?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:31.80,sign_33758_316_Episode_16___Bun,Sign 2330,0,0,0,,Episode 16 \N Bungo Stray Dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:34.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それは書類を裁判所に届けるだけの簡単な仕事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:36.99,sign_33758_316_Episode_16___Bu2,Sign 2330,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}And the story resumes,\Nfour years later
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,…のはずだったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:41.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私が得意なのは色仕掛けで人気のない処に誘い込んでから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:39.99,sign_31802_310_Next_Time__Episo,Sign 2207,0,0,0,,Next Time: Episode 17\N Three Companies {\c&H0300E0&}Con{\c&H000000&}flict
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:42.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐさりと刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:43.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それはもう忘れなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:47.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな鏡花ちゃんを追って現れるポートマフィアの追手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:51.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　さらにどんでもない敵が現れた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:55.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,次回　文豪ストレイドッグス　第十七話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:57.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,三社鼎立
